column5: ANy reports from this area yet....I am heading up there in Feb.  Pm me if necessary!
was up in the Bancroft area on the weekend. About 6 inches on the lake I fished. Got one 4 lb laker and lost another.
Where's the pic ATF  I was going up there to scout some property ... hoping to take a side trip for some back-lake specks  PM me if you're up for it
The speck bite was on in early Jan. I haven't heard and reports lately but the ice is alot better now and its opens the area up for more fishing.
You guys and wanting to see pics. Jeez  I don't have a digital camera so no pics right now.
